        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #7f8c8d; word-break: break-all;">${assetUrl}</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #667eea;">📱 扫码进入领用表单页面</p>
